      "span_text": "In a recent phase 2 trial of REGN-727 in patients with heterozygous familial hypercholesterolemia and LDL-C concentrations of at least 2.6 mmol/l on a stable diet, REGN-727 was well tolerated and reduced LDL-C by 28.9-67.9% in various doses"
